Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.25,0:00:01.38,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,That smells good.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.90,0:00:03.90,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.16,0:00:06.72,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,How is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.68,0:00:11.80,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,Looks as if you don’t like it, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.05,0:00:12.70,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,Too bitter?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.92,0:00:13.78,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,What if you add some sugar?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.82,0:00:16.76,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,Well, how about if you add some milk?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.76,0:00:18.66,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,It might take away the bitterness.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.40,0:00:21.00,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,Or I can get you something else?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.00,0:00:23.18,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,I don’t like milk.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.73,0:00:31.66,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,Ah, sorry. I didn’t know... Well, how about if I get some juice for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.21,0:00:35.97,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,I’m sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.18,0:00:41.06,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,That’s all right; I probably couldn’t have had green tea either at your age.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.18,0:00:46.30,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,You said that there are lots of different kinds of tea right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.78,0:00:48.64,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,If I don’t like it, I don’t like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.40,0:00:57.30,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,Of course, that doesn’t mean I can’t drink it, but different kinds of tea have different flavors right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.20,0:01:00.82,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,What do you like, Lain?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.13,0:01:03.80,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,Why don’t you like milk?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.46,0:01:06.16,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,It upsets my stomach.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.29,0:01:11.40,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, truth be told, when I was a child I had the same problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.98,0:01:17.05,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,Especially when the school lunch included milk, I can drink milk now though.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.08,0:01:19.53,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,I can’t drink it, but I really love it...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.64,0:01:23.13,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,How about milk that doesn’t upset your stomach? Would that be all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.96,0:01:25.13,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,What’s it called?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.14,0:01:30.66,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,I forgot what it’s called, but it’s milk that doesn’t upset your stomach.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.52,0:01:34.92,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,I have it for kids like you Lain, who are like me as a kid and can’t drink milk.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.85,0:01:38.60,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,If you talk about it with your mother, I’m sure she’ll look for it for you.
